text: Sheena Mackintosh (10 November 1928 - 13 December 2018) was a British alpine skier. She competed in two events at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:2018 deaths Category:British female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Great Britain Category:Alpine skiers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:Alpine skiers at the 1952 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from London
